README
------

To build the sword bindings for Sword you require

SWIG 1.3 (see http://www.swig.org)
one of perl, python, tcl, php
Sword 1.5.8 or newer

First run
./autogen.sh
./configure

Then, e.g.,:

make perlswig
make perl_make
cd perl
sudo make install

or

make pythonswig
make python_make
cd python
sudo python setup.py install


